org.baswell.routes

Class RequestParameters

  • java.lang.Object
    • org.baswell.routes.RequestParameters

  • public class RequestParameters
extends java.lang.Object
    The parameters from an HTTP request. Default parameters for a route (Route.defaultParameters()) will be present for any parameters not explicitly set in the HTTP request.
